# NEXUS — AI Executive Agent Network

> A proof-of-concept for AI-to-AI opportunity matching between executive agents.

![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-0.1.0-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green)
