## The Concept

Imagine every executive had a personal AI assistant that already knew their strategic priorities, deal preferences, and mandate. Now imagine those AI assistants could talk to each other — screening, matching, and evaluating opportunities at machine speed — and only escalating to the human when something genuinely warrants their attention.

That’s NEXUS.

No more cold emails lost in inboxes. No more great opportunities buried under noise. AI agents negotiate the first filter, humans close the deal.

-----

## How It Works

```
[Opportunity Holder] ──► AGENT ALPHA ──► NEXUS Protocol ──► AGENT BETA ──► [Executive]
        │                   │                  │                  │               │
   Inputs their          Broadcasts         Agent-to-agent     Screens against   Sees only
   opportunity           profile            handshake          principal         high-match
   details                                  & evaluation       mandate           opportunities
```

1. **Agent Alpha** represents the opportunity holder — broadcasts deal profile, sector tags, and deal type
1. **Agent Beta** represents the receiving executive — screens against their strategic mandate
1. **Match Score** is generated (0–100) with escalation decision
1. **Escalation** — only high-match opportunities reach the human

