## Demo

The `/demo` folder contains a standalone HTML demo you can open in any browser. It uses the Claude API to power real AI evaluation.

### Quick Start

1. Clone this repo
   
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/nexus-agent-network.git
   cd nexus-agent-network
   ```
1. Open `demo/index.html` in your browser
1. Add your Claude API key in `config.js` (see setup below)
1. Configure both agents and click **INITIATE AGENT-TO-AGENT HANDSHAKE**

